History:

v0.71
Improved firmware
- Got rid of third party code.
- New time keeper using counter1 and fatstest algoritm for alamrs. Still needs a resume function.
- New TWI interface using interrupts, including wraps for ds1307. It is readinf, WIP for writing.

v0.7
First implementation with Arduino, an ugly firmware written in C using third party code.

v0.6
This implementation uses an old PC and its parallel port.
Written on Perl, it has a web interface and uses motion to control a webcam.
